     Springtime in Europe!  Announcing Group Specials to Europe

US Airways is offering special sale fares for groups of ten or more passengers traveling together from the continental U.S. to Europe between April 1, 2002 and May 31, 2002. Group reservations must be made through US Airways Group & Meeting Travel at 877-US GROUPS (877-874-7687) no later than 30 days prior to departure, or by Friday, March 15, 2002, whichever is earliest.  Or, visit us at http://www.usairways.com/groups/europe_group_sale.htm

Call US Airways Group & Meeting Travel between 8:30 a.m. and 6:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, to make your group reservation or for more information on these and other group specials.

